{"tid":81330,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老尾,啱啱踢波,我諗我破左個紀錄","createTime":"2017-01-15T08:42:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T15:12:18.000Z","uid":73934,"like":2,"dislike":151,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5ae94fe7a7f6e3e5658e349eb1381f67b2ff3e82","tid":81330,"uid":73934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:42:03.000Z","msg":"啱先一開波,個中圈既人就傳比我(我打右閘)咁有人埋黎迫,<br />\n我穩陣派緊係回傳比個龍,我回傳個陣時,突然諗到黃興桂曾經講過,<br />\n傳比龍個陣千其唔好兕口兕臉直傳,要斜少少咁龍門先易攞同即刻清到<br />\n咁個龍企近柱,我就斜少少傳番去遠柱啦,但係角度太靓,個龍又呆撚左唔識反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,球波就咁就好似人單刀射遠柱咁,慢流尾到袋仲要中內柱入埋,成個過程5秒都冇,跟住成班仆街連睇波阿伯,全部笑到反艇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,問我係咪破左最快鳥龍球記錄,仲叫我去申請健力士,我屌你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b45341342ed8ca31077e0eed658eb6da1b7da0","tid":81330,"uid":3344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:44:32.000Z","msg":"屌你老母殘體字"},{"pid":"37abd60fa278983fe8f4d272c33f18ea2d58f4af","tid":81330,"uid":52994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:44:40.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"56566115684aecb41345d33d9cd5db69f5dc54b6","tid":81330,"uid":2470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:49:54.000Z","msg":"粒lin尚健在嗎？"},{"pid":"3ea78ca5f7a14865da3e7f3c634bc374dd970b2c","tid":81330,"uid":73934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:52:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母殘體字</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母邊撚度有呀"},{"pid":"c0ddd9d5fd388aaeb7e8d69ba272b499c4493774","tid":81330,"uid":73934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:53:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>閱</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n閱你老母"},{"pid":"c91e38103298c0ebac2c29e525e9cfd5ffac5218","tid":81330,"uid":73934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:53:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>粒lin尚健在嗎？</bloc